Scale class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "AreaClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The Scale class is used to create a numbered scale.

  Note that despite a Scale object is quite always used with a
  Gauge object, it may be put after any object.

  See @{"MakeObj()" LINK "Functions.guide/MakeObj"}.

